      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON LIZZIE (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (32.10) in a Grade 6 at Angle Park. Solid record here at this trip including three wins. Rates on top in this line up. DIRTY DASH (2) goes very well this course and distance starting eight times for three wins and four minors. Missed the frame latest (23.30) when fifth over 400m at Gawler in a Invitation. Can feature in the finish. APPELLANT (1) ran below best last time finishing fifth (23.63) over 400m at this track from Box 8. Has a strong record from box 1, including two wins. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. CHEQUES TO BURN (6) was impressive in an excellent 17.45 win last start. Each way chance.",
